    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hotels constructed on a river, lake, or off the coast. For large ships with hotel accommodations and the primary activity of taking tourists on extended excursions, use "cruise ships."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
